children.description: When I select Physician from Professional Category dropdown
Then Price of IM is $650.00
Then Price of FM is $650.00
Then Price of PD is $650.00
And I Select PD Checkbox
And I click Continue Button
Then I add first name as kplustestqa
Then I add last name
Then I add Address as 352 Mansfield Road
Then I add city as Storrs
Then I select country as UNITED STATES OF AMERICA
Then I select state as CONNECTICUT
Then I add zip code as 06269
Then I select place of work or study as Other
Then I select speciality as Addiction
Then I add user account information
Then I add card information
Then Verify Tax amount added is $6.50
And I click Submit Button
Then Purchase Confirmation Page Displays
And I click your profile link
Then Verify Welcome Message
Then I download the Receipt
Then Receipt contains $656.50
